    body
      // Header
      header
        .container
            .divider
                .logo
                    a(href="./").logo
                        span Talk Push Logo
                    a(href="#").menu-button
                        i(class="fa fa-bars",aria-hidden="true")
                .menu
                    include ./_navigation.pug

      .display-header.whatsapp
        .filter
            .container
                .divider
                    .left
                        .holder: img(src="./images/whatsapp.png", alt="WhatsApp")
                        a(href="https://web.whatsapp.com/send?phone=+16502812190&text=hi", target="_blank")
                            i(class="fa fa-whatsapp",aria-hidden="true")
                            span Try it now
                    .right
                        h1 WhatsApp
                        p You’ve been asking for it for years… Finally WhatsApp is opening its API for business accounts! Talkpush is working with Nexmo to integrate its CRM with WhatsApp. This means your business can finally access 1.5 billion WhatsApp users!


      #crm-building.white-theme
        .container
          .filter
            h2.gl.whatsapp Reach 1.5 billion active users
            p.gl WhatsApp Business + Talkpush CRM = an enjoyable candidate experience.
            .divide
              .image
                .holder: img(src="./images/whatsapp-user.png", alt="Building")
              .content.whatsapp
                p Talkpush CRM was designed for messaging. It was initially built to support SMS/Text messaging, and later added the integration with Facebook Messenger as soon as the API became available (summer 2016). 
                p We believe that employers have a responsibility to treat candidates with the same love and care as they treat customers. This starts with designing a recruitment process which makes the life of their candidates simple.  Offering candidates a digital assistant which can direct their applications via their favorite messaging app is a big step in the right direction.

      #crm-ai.dark-theme
        .container
          .filter
            h2.gl Meet your talent where it lives
            p.gl Being candidate-centric begings with being available
            .divide.reverse
              .image
                .holder(style="background-color: transparent; border-width: 0;box-shadow: none;"): img(src="./images/whatsapp-phone.png", alt="WhatsApp Phone", style="max-width: 20rem;")
              .content.whatsapp
                h2 Meet your talent where it lives
                p Of course, making it easier for candidates to reach you is a no brainer. When you remove barriers between you and your talent pool, you can expect your numbers to grow and that comes with a few challenges:
                ul
                    li How do you get back to everyone in time?
                    li How can you direct the incoming inquiries to the right jobs?
                    li How can you answer all their questions?
                p By integrating your WhatsApp Business account with your Talkpush CRM you are able to sort, screen and engage with a large volume of talent while maintaining a positive experience, with a short response time, a personalized and customized candidate experience, and a direct link to your recruitment team. With Talkpush you can funnel your applicants from social media, job boards, career pages, employee referrals and more directly to WhatsApp.  Click <a href="https://calendly.com/talkpush-demo/talkpush-intro-demo" target="_blank">here to schedule a demo of the Talkpush CRM</a> (to see how to implement it alongside your Whatsapp Business account).

      .whatsapp-form-holder
        .container
            h2.gl Request a WhatsApp Business account for recruitment
            form.whatsapp-form
                // Full Name
                input(type="text", name="name", placeholder="Full Name")
                // E-mail
                input(type="text", name="email", placeholder="E-mail")
                // Phone Number
                input(type="text", name="phone", placeholder="Phone Number")
                // Company Name
                input(type="text", name="company", placeholder="Company Name")
                // Recruitment Volume
                input(list="whatsapp-form-volume", name="volume", placeholder="Annual Recruitment Volume")
                datalist#whatsapp-form-volume
                    option(value="1-100")
                    option(value="100-1000")
                    option(value="1000-10000")
                    option(value="More than 10k")
                .whatsapp-form-ending
                    // In Touch Button
                    input#whatsapp-form-in-touch(type="checkbox", name="in-touch", value="In Touch")
                    label(for="whatsapp-form-in-touch") I would like to stay in touch with Talkpush through digital communication.<br />You may opt-out at anytime by sending us an unsubscribe request.
                    // Submit Button
                    button(type="submit")
                        i(class="fa fa-send-o",aria-hidden="true")
                        span Submit

